fields.name: Anthony
fields.bio: Anthony from Kiev, was working in aviation for ~10 years recently decide to became a programmer and after passing programming trainings (approx. 2 years long) which are tyghty related with self-improvement via practice on solving different kinds of most common programming problems. I've recently started my way as programmer, and i do clearly understand that my experiance in the real projects is prety poor, but i hope to have a possibility to earn it in any way.
